dc_title_s: Plan de la ville et faubourgs de Paris: avec tous ses accroissmens et la nouvell enceinte des barrieres de ctte capitale.
dc_description_s: Inlcudes index to streets and places of interest and inset of paris region. Map may be a reprint of an earlier ed. by L.F. DeHarme, 1763. 1 map; 61 x 94 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
